text: That Time of Year () is a 2018 Danish comedy film directed by Paprika Steen. It was screened in the Contemporary World Cinema section at the 2018 Toronto International Film Festival. ==Cast== * Sofie Gråbøl as Barbara * Paprika Steen as Katrine * Lars Brygmann as Torben * Jacob Lohmann as Mads * Lars Knutzon as Poul ==References== ==External links== * Category:2018 films Category:2018 comedy films Category:Danish films Category:Danish comedy films Category:Danish-language films
title: That Time of Year
